&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Make a difference with us! At Alliance Defending Freedom, we believe God has brought you here for His purpose—to stand for truth and defend the God-given right to live and speak it. Together, we protect religious freedom, free speech, the sanctity of life, marriage and family, and parental rights. Review our &lt;a href=&quot;https://adflegal.org/about-us/careers/statement-of-faith/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Statement of Faith&lt;/a&gt; to ensure we’re a fit for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: rgb(35, 111, 161);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 48, 87);&quot;&gt;Locations:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Lansdowne, VA; Scottsdale, AZ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: rgb(0, 48, 87);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;In this role you will be responsible for executing new member sales strategies to grow membership and partnership relationships in Alliance Defending Freedom&#39;s Church &amp;amp; Ministry Alliance. This includes identifying potential members, conveying the high value of membership benefits, building relationships, networking, and ensuring the success of the membership onboarding process. You will also execute member engagement strategies to meet the needs and retain existing members. Your role is instrumental in ensuring members and prospects understand the value of CMA membership: building relationships, educating members, and encouraging participation with ADF to keep the door open for the Gospel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: rgb(0, 48, 87);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;122&quot; data-end=&quot;163&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;122&quot; data-end=&quot;163&quot;&gt;New Membership Development and Sales:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot; data-start=&quot;122&quot; data-end=&quot;163&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Proactively develop and manage a diverse portfolio of prospective and current members through strong sales acumen, customer-focused strategies, and excellent communication and organizational skills.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot; data-start=&quot;122&quot; data-end=&quot;163&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Create and execute in-person and virtual relationship-building opportunities to meet sales goals, support ministry growth, and strengthen CMA’s presence within key communities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot; data-start=&quot;122&quot; data-end=&quot;163&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Lead outreach strategies by developing pipelines through referrals, cold and warm leads, and both assigned and self-initiated contacts; conduct targeted calls, emails, and follow-ups to educate and engage prospects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot; data-start=&quot;122&quot; data-end=&quot;163&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Coordinate and deliver CMA presentations, webinars, events, and educational offerings for prospective and current members, including attendance at denominational gatherings and ministry events.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Make a difference with us! At Alliance Defending Freedom, we believe God has brought you here for His purpose—to stand for truth and defend the God-given right to live and speak it. Together, we protect religious freedom, free speech, the sanctity of life, marriage and family, and parental rights. Review our &lt;a href=&quot;https://adflegal.org/about-us/careers/statement-of-faith/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Statement of Faith&lt;/a&gt; to ensure we’re a fit for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: rgb(35, 111, 161);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 48, 87);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Lansdowne, VA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: rgb(0, 48, 87);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;In this role, you will report to the Vice President of Communications and PR and are responsible for managing the creation of speeches, briefing documents, op-eds, and other content for ADF’s CEO, President and Chief Counsel, and other senior leaders as needed; overseeing research and information gathering for reports for executive leadership, donors and key stakeholders, collaborating with the Vice President of Communications on messaging, statements, and other communications content.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: rgb(0, 48, 87);&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Develop executive communications (speeches, briefing documents, op-eds, presentations, statements, etc.) primarily for the CEO, President and Chief Counsel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Prepare and/or edit messaging documents for internal and external communications.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Develop periodic summaries and presentations for the Board of Directors.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Translate objectives, team performance, and organizational vision into stories and messages that relate to specific audiences.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Oversee and coordinate research and information-gathering related to ADF cases and Legal and Communications team performance for reports for executive leadership, donors, and key stakeholders, and for speeches and remarks delivered by the CEO, President and Chief Counsel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Maintain a database of material for use in speeches and op-eds.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain a library system cataloging speeches, presentations, and media appearances delivered by the CEO, President and General Counsel, and other spokespeople.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
