&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Make a difference with us! At Alliance Defending Freedom, we believe God has brought you here for His purpose—to stand for truth and defend the God-given right to live and speak it. Together, we protect religious freedom, free speech, the sanctity of life, marriage and family, and parental rights. Review our&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://adflegal.org/about-us/careers/statement-of-faith/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Statement of Faith&lt;/a&gt; to ensure we’re a fit for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
