&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;In this part-time role, you will report to the DC Facilities Manager and are responsible for providing an exceptional experience for Team Members and guests at the Plano, TX office. This position will function as the main point of contact for on-site facilities maintenance, vendor relations, purchasing, and event support and will oversee the day-to-day facility operations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
