&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif; color: rgb(0, 48, 87);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Conduct research and interview clients and witnesses&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Prepare and respond to written discovery; conduct and defend depositions&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Represent clients in court, and before quasi-judicial or administrative agencies of government; interpret laws, rulings, and regulations for individuals and businesses&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
