&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: georgia, palatino, serif;&quot;&gt;Advise allied attorneys on legal issues within areas of competence&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
